  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when I walk under-- you know, towards him, I was so young, but I felt like I thought this marriage will be 100% happy because I want it this way.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I really believe that a woman has lots to say about the wedding, you know, and the marriage.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So then we-- he was, of course, working for the Jewish agency.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we moved to Innsbruck, as I say, because less and less people stayed in the place, the hachshara.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So then after we got the papers, we had a good time in Innsbruck, OK?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There is nothing to complain about it because, well, never mind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I cannot keep you so much and so long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But-- but then-- How long were you Innsbruck--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Innsbruck?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The wedding was-- I'll tell you how long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The wedding was in '46, and this was September.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were there maybe two months before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we arrived here in '49.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "End of August.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With-- oh.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
